Filterbuffer pcb

Hardware Design: 

Dan Olson 
Copyright 2019

This board is currently is testing phase, use at your own risk.

This is a board designed to facilitate the filtering of high frequency line noise spikes and provide a voltage buffer to 48v power supplies. Is is meant to connect to power mosfets.

Typical uses:

Audio equipment
Industrial control systems
Pinball machines

Features:

Two large capacitor units.
48v power led.
In-rush current limitor.
250v safety fuse.
Two independent non-filtered sections for powering 12v and 5v systems.

